Package: maplamina
Title: High-Performance 'WebGL' Mapping Widgets for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jack", "Humble", email = "jackhumble.dev@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates interactive maps using 'MapLibre GL' and 'deck.gl' via 'htmlwidgets'.
    Provides GPU-accelerated layers for points, lines and polygons, plus linked user interface
    components such as filters, views and summary cards for exploratory analysis and
    production dashboards.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jhumbl/maplamina, https://jhumbl.github.io/maplamina/
BugReports: https://github.com/jhumbl/maplamina/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    htmlwidgets,
    digest,
    base64enc,
    sf
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    jsonlite
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
